## Lifecycle

### Session Start
1. integration-check verifies environment
2. Briefing displays machine status, recent work, incomplete items
3. hub-watcher checks for framework updates and signals
4. Agent loads WAI context (State, BRIEF, Skills)

### During Session
- Signals fire based on events (complexity, context, stewardship)
- Skills guard/review/advise as work progresses
- Observations recorded to observations.jsonl
- Session log captures conversation

### Session End
1. session-observer synthesizes session summary
2. closeout_validator checks git, observations, framework health
3. Optional: /shipit commits with summary
4. Session Lug created for next briefing

